@myeveryheart do you mean that any implements you need are not in the public_header_files yet? Can you describe it in more detail? Thanks.

Weex 的代码一直在更新，参考这里： https://github.com/apache/incubator-weex/pulse/monthly

> July 13, 2018 – August 13, 2018
>
> Excluding merges, 19 authors have pushed 84 commits to master and 93 commits to all branches. On master, 238 files have changed and there have been 13,389 additions and 1,138 deletions.
@xuyouyang Yes, you are right. Cocoapods can create public headers If no public headers are specified then all the headers in source_files are considered public. That would be better.

@myeveryheart I am sorry that I maybe not agree with you. In my opinions, a SDK framework do not need to public every file, such as some inner utility files. If you want to use or add more implements, you can add 'Category' files in your own project. Furthermore, you can import Weex source code to your project and public anything you want through local pod.

Weex 编译js的时候会自动添加一个

# 但是只是解决不报错
一般报 `using unregister weex module` 是因为用了没注册的原生模块。按照文档[自定义模块](http://weex-project.io/cn/guide/extend-ios.html#zi-ding-yi-module)里的介绍，除了写一份模块实现以外，还要在初始化好 Weex SDK 之后注册一下自定义的模块，这样页面里才能调用得到。
某些资源文件配置的 HTTP 缓存时间有问题，如果某些时候浏览器缓存了有问题的文件，就会一直有问题，除非缓存过期。这些问题后续会修复一下。
Please offer an example on http://dotwe.org/vue to reproduce it.
你好，这类问题欢迎在其他问答社区中提问。可以自行对比社区中专门做推送功能的 SDK，基本上都可以集成进 Weex。

我以把问题视频发送到你zhanghan.me@gmail.com的邮箱
附件包括: 问题修复前视频录屏，修复后视频录屏，修复前后weexSDK中WXDatePickerManager.m中修改的代码截图，使用的vue文件，
目前只测试出当前的这个iPhone7 Plus有这个问题，其他的机型暂未发现此问题
望查收邮件并关注此问题

@WeibinZheng 我本人是前端开发，解决不了 iOS 相关的问题，你可以直接在 issue 里贴出来，这样大家都可以看到。

建议把复现问题的代码贴到 http://dotwe.org/ 里，涉及到的原生代码直接贴在 issue 里（GitHub 也支持传文件），并且介绍一下复现过程。
@Hanks10100 should be closed, no longer active issue.
@kyriediculous please provide your examples on http://dotwe.org/
@Hanks10100 issue should be close ~

Or you think Apple will not know a private method swizzling if you split the method name string?
